code: import md5 from"md5";function clean(url){return url.replace(/^.+\/api/,"");}function getPrefix(url){return clean(url).replace(/\?.+$/,'').replace(/\//,'').replace(/\//g,'_').replace(".json",'');}export function urlToFilename(username,url){return"".concat(getPrefix(url),"_").concat(md5(username+clean(url)));}
